08:27.210 --> 08:29.150
The unsub may be out
of his comfort zone.

08:29.170 --> 08:31.740
Now,they may not all be connected,but
they all match michelle's type.

08:31.770 --> 08:34.020
Blond,white,eay 30s.

08:34.059 --> 08:37.030
The autopsy reports will help us determine
which of these cases is connected.

08:37.070 --> 08:38.150
I'll get them here right away.

08:38.190 --> 08:40.370
We also need to take a look at the
crime scenes,detective henderson.

08:40.390 --> 08:41.200
Of course.

08:41.230 --> 08:42.480
I'll stay and help reid.

08:42.500 --> 08:44.240
I'll take prentiss and morgan.

08:48.770 --> 08:52.700
Tell me,do you think this is a
one off or can I expect more films?

08:52.750 --> 08:56.710
